@startuml
title 歌手认证审核时序图

actor 管理员 as Admin
participant "ArtistController(管理员)" as Ctrl
participant "ArtistService" as Svc
participant "ArtistMapper" as ArtistMapper
participant "ArtistAuthMapper" as AuthMapper
database "MySQL" as DB

Admin -> Ctrl: 审核结果
activate Ctrl

Ctrl -> Svc: artistAuth(artistAuthDTO)
activate Svc

Svc -> ArtistMapper: 查询歌手是否存在
DB --> Svc: 返回artist

alt 歌手不存在
    Svc --> Admin: 歌手不存在
else 歌手已认证
    Svc --> Admin: 歌手已经认证
else 认证申请已取消
    Svc --> Admin: 歌手已经取消认证
else 其他情况
    alt status == 0 (取消认证)
        Svc -> AuthMapper: 更新认证申请状态
        Svc --> Admin: 取消认证成功
    else status == 1 (通过认证)
        Svc -> ArtistMapper: 更新歌手userId
        Svc -> AuthMapper: 更新认证申请状态
        Svc --> Admin: 认证成功
    end
end

deactivate Svc
deactivate Ctrl

@enduml
